According to a report by Intel Market Research, the global Espresso Machines Market was valued at USD 3.34 billion in 2024 and is projected to grow from USD 3.55 billion in 2025 to USD 5.13 billion by 2032, registering a CAGR of 6.5% during the forecast period. The market is witnessing robust growth due to the increasing popularity of specialty coffee, the rising trend of creating café-style beverages at home, and continuous technological advancements in smart espresso machines. Growing café culture, higher disposable incomes, and expanding demand from both residential and commercial users are further supporting market expansion worldwide.
